[{"id":"37f28fbce9a7cb38ed0c6f0b95d93b41","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: Save the Date for...","date":"2008-03-04T13:32:56.000Z","formatted_date":"Mar 4, 2008","formatted_time":"1:32 PM","body":" \n\n \n\nFrom: BEHNBOM@aol.com [mailto:BEHNBOM@aol.com] \nSent: Monday, March 03, 2008 5:52 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: Save the Date for...\n\n \n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n\n\nWELCOME TO SALSS 2008\n\n\nSWEDISH-AMERICAN LIFE SCIENCE SUMMIT\n\nAugust 20-22, 2008 in Stockholm, Sweden\n\n \n\nSAVE THE DATE\n\nThe 4th annual Swedish-American Life Science Summit will take place in Stockholm, August 20-22, 2008. Please mark your calendar for one of the most exceptional life science events of the year. Details will follow in early May. Continuous information updates soon to be found at our website, www.swedishamericanlifescience.com <http://www.swedishamericanlifescience.com/> . Please contact Project Coordinator Freja Langert-Gid\u00e9n for any inquiries at freja@swedishamericanlifescience.com or at +4670 279 2524.\n\nV\u00e4lkommen! \n\nBarbro C. Ehnbom \n\n \n\n \n\n\n\n\n\n________________________________\n\nIt's Tax Time! Get tips, forms and advice on AOL Money & Finance. <http://money.aol.com/tax?NCID=aolprf00030000000001> \n\n\n\n\n\n________________________________\n\nIt's Tax Time! Get tips, forms and advice on AOL Money & Finance. <http://money.aol.com/tax?NCID=aolprf00030000000001> \n\n","body_html":"<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Content-Type\" CONTENT=\"text/html; charset=iso-8859-1\">\n<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:m=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\">\n\n<head>\n\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 12 (filtered medium)\">\n<!--[if !mso]>\n<style>\nv\\:* {be